Back in the day.

00:01:42.560 --> 00:01:45.040
Back in the day was like three
years ago, four years ago.

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:46.260
That was a lot to get.

00:01:46.260 --> 00:01:49.310
Today, I have like two tera and
I'm paying ten bucks.

