And by earning that virtual currency,
by earning those things that

00:02:48.050 --> 00:02:53.450
you want in order to pursue your dreams,
they can encourage this behavior.

00:02:53.450 --> 00:02:55.790
Another example is Lyft.

00:02:55.790 --> 00:02:59.380
Lyft is competing with Uber in many
geographies throughout the US and

00:02:59.380 --> 00:03:00.718
throughout the world.

00:03:00.718 --> 00:03:06.650
And Lyft wants to get more market share,
how can they do that?

00:03:06.650 --> 00:03:11.770
One of the strategies is to
pay you to ride with them.

00:03:11.770 --> 00:03:16.780
So let's say I want to get from point
A to point B in Manhattan and this

00:03:16.780 --> 00:03:23.215
is a ride that will cost me with Uber
20 bucks, with a yellow cab, 15 bucks.

00:03:23.215 --> 00:03:26.220
Lyft will give you money
to ride with them so

00:03:26.220 --> 00:03:29.140
it will cost you five bucks,
