00:03:29.140 --> 00:03:33.970
In this way, they can encourage the
behavior that they want to encourage,

00:03:33.970 --> 00:03:39.090
that forming a habit,
if you associated Lyft with

00:03:39.090 --> 00:03:44.210
taking a cab by encouraging you and
giving you money to use them.

