One major thing that you need to be
very cautious about when you're doing

00:03:48.340 --> 00:03:52.660
incentive problem is making
sure that your lifetime value,

00:03:52.660 --> 00:03:56.910
your LTV, is higher than your
customer acquisition cost, your CAC.

00:03:56.910 --> 00:03:59.950
A lot of companies tend to

00:04:01.290 --> 00:04:05.630
exaggerate with acquiring users,
focusing on growth,

00:04:05.630 --> 00:04:09.730
